1. *Brojač* na struju se pokvario. (The *counter* on the electricity meter is broken.)
2. On ima ogroman *broj* knjiga u svojoj biblioteci. (He has a huge *number* of books in his library.)
3. Naš tim je postigao *brojne* pobede tokom sezone. (Our team achieved *numerous* victories during the season.)
4. *Brojimo* na tebe da ćeš doći na našu proslavu. (We *count* on you to come to our celebration.)
5. On je *broj* jedan teniser u svetu. (He is the *number* one tennis player in the world.)
6. U matematici, *broj* 7 se piše kao VII u rimskim brojevima. (In mathematics, the *number* 7 is written as VII in Roman numerals.)
7. Da li možeš da mi kažeš *broj* telefona vaše kancelarije? (Can you tell me the *phone number* of your office?)
8. *Brojevi* na lutriji su izvučeni sinoć. (The *numbers* in the lottery were drawn last night.)
9. Danas smo *brojali* ovce kako bismo lakše zaspali. (Today we *counted* sheep to help us fall asleep.)
10. Molim vas, navedite *broj* vaše polise osiguranja. (Please provide the *policy number* of your insurance.)